{
  "stem": "11998.6",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We were not allowed to get rid of the-- the bodies, so we had to-- we lined them along the outside of the car, the cattle car.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we covered them with straw, and we sat on them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And there was lots of room, by the time we arrived in-- in Flossenburg, which was seven days later.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they never stopped for-- we stopped-- you know, they-- we were traveling and stopping, and traveling and stopping.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Most of the time, we were traveling at night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And the Nazis were making sure that nobody had even the strength to-- to jump out of this-- the railroad car.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "You know, the railroad car was way over your head.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Nobody could-- even had the strength to chin themself up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And when we got to Flossenburg, there were very few of us left in the car.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we had to walk up the hill, which was a very strenuous march.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was about February-- beginning of February, 1945.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was cold, but we didn't-- I don't even remember-- I don't remember even being cold, for some reason or other.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we went-- we got to Flossenburg, and we were put into-- we got there in the evening, in the dark.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was already nightfall, and-- or-- or it was getting dusk, dark.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they put us in this big, huge shower room, this huge shower room.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were sort of looking at these things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we're looking to see if there's any holes where they would throw the gas into.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we didn't know whether this was it, or whether this was just a regular shower.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we stay-- stayed there the whole night in that shower, not knowing what they're going to do for us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were naked and cold.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
